OL,5, Virgil Abloh, the Louis Vuitton        
OL,6, artistic director and founder of the   
OL,7, Off-White fashion label, has died from 
OL,8, cancer aged 41, it has been announced. 
OL,10,FRevealing the news, the French fashion 
OL,11,Fhouse's parent company LVMH described  
OL,12,FAbloh as a "genius" and a "visionary". 
OL,14,FThe US designer came to prominence as  
OL,15,FKanye West's creative director but     
OL,16,Flater made history as the first        
OL,17,FAfrican-American to lead Louis Vuitton.
OL,19,FAbloh is survived by his wife, Shannon,
OL,20,Fand their two children.                
